      <div class="block__section">
        <p>Big Change Manchester aims to help rough sleepers get off and stay off the streets.</p>
        <p>A group of charities and organisations has teamed up to create a special ‘essentials’ fund which is used to provide homeless people with practical items they need to build new lives off the streets.</p>
        <p>The campaign encourages people who live in, work in and visit the city centre to donate money to the fund if they want to help rough sleepers, rather than give money to people who are begging.</p>

        <p class="text-center">
          <a href="http://campaign.justgiving.com/charity/forevermanchester/bigchangemcr" class="btn btn--brand-e btn--full">
