        <h2 class="h2">Why is this better than giving money on the streets?</h2>
        <p>Those who provide support to rough sleepers advise that giving money to people who are begging isn't an effective way to help people move away from the streets. By giving money via this network of experts, you can be sure that your donation will go directly to meet the needs of individuals that really need it.</p>

